HTML 
1) All tags must be closed.
2) Value of attributes must be in Double Quote ("")
3) whenever applying css classes, use className instead of class
4) if you are using image ( first import image as js variable) and alt attribute is must.
5) you cannot render multiple elements directly. (use <div> or <>)

